# opkg repository with VDR for OE ${OE_VERSION}
This is the opkg repository providing VDR for OE-Linux ${OE_VERSION}

## Supported platform:
These packages are compiled for the following platform:

Distro: ${DISTRO}\
Machine: ${MACHINE}\
